# 2.82

A. 0.(y) = Y / ( 2^k - 1 )





















B. (a) 101    -> 5/7
   (b) 0110   -> 6/15 = 2/5
   (c) 010011 -> 19/63
   

# 2.87

		Format A							Format B
  Bits			Value					Bits		Value
1 01111 001		 -9/8			    1 0111 0010 	 -9/8
0 10110 011	     176				0 1110 0110		 176
1 00111 010	     -5/2^10			1 0000 0101	 	-5/2^10
0 00000 111		 7/2^16				0 0000 0001		1/2^10   (*)
1 11100 000		 -2^13				1 1110 1111		248		 (*)
0 10111 100		 3*2^7				0 1111 0000		inf		 (*)















